The sharp turn entry generates when a bullish FVG appears after a bearish one (going long) or when a bearish FVG appears after a bullish one (going short), but only on confirmed bars that mark a new 4-hour period. I need to be careful about how the lastFVG state updates—it changes whenever an FVG forms, not just on entries, so the tracking needs to reflect that behavior accurately.

